CREATE TABLE `lineitem` (
  `l_shipdate` datev2 NOT NULL,
  `l_orderkey` bigint(20) NOT NULL,
  `l_linenumber` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `l_partkey` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `l_suppkey` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `l_quantity` decimal(15, 2) NOT NULL,
  `l_extendedprice` decimal(15, 2) NOT NULL,
  `l_discount` decimal(15, 2) NOT NULL,
  `l_tax` decimal(15, 2) NOT NULL,
  `l_returnflag` varchar(1) NOT NULL,
  `l_linestatus` varchar(1) NOT NULL,
  `l_commitdate` datev2 NOT NULL,
  `l_receiptdate` datev2 NOT NULL,
  `l_shipinstruct` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `l_shipmode` varchar(10) NOT NULL,
  `l_comment` varchar(44) NOT NULL
) ENGINE=OLAP
DUPLICATE KEY(`l_shipdate`, `l_orderkey`)
COMMENT 'OLAP'
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(`l_orderkey`) BUCKETS 96
PROPERTIES (
"replication_allocation" = "tag.location.default: 1",
"colocate_with" = "lineitem_orders",
"in_memory" = "false",
"storage_format" = "V2",
"disable_auto_compaction" = "false"
);

``` SQL
select
    a.app_name, a.user_id, b.province
from
    (
        -- group by400w
        select 
            app_name
            ,user_id 
        from 
            test_duplicate_table
        where 
            server_timestamp between '2022-11-02 00:00:00' and '2022-11-03 00:00:00'
        group by 
            app_name
            ,user_id
    ) a
left join
    (
        select 
            app_name
            ,user_id
            ,max(province) as province
        from 
            test_duplicate_table
        where 
            server_timestamp between '2022-11-02 00:00:00' and '2022-11-03 00:00:00'
        group by 
            app_name
            ,user_id
    ) b on b.user_id = a.user_id and b.app_name = a.app_name
limit 10
```
